page.title: 11Club <Gym club.>
page.content: I am very interested in gym club.There are two gym clubs Broadwindsor and Beaminster. At Broadwinser we have floor and vault work. We have got a spring board and it goes up by the vault, which is when you jump on to the spring board and put your hands on the vault and jump over the vault then try to land on your feet. These are some of the vaults l do, through vault, straddle vault, hand spring, headspring and neck spring. On the floor I do lots of moves like rolls walkovers etc. Gym is fun and it makes you work very hard.At Beaminster Ihave four piece which is beam,bar, floor and vault.Beam I do balances,splits etc.On the bar I do up starts,swings to the bar etc.Floor and vault Iv,e already explained but I do much harder moves on the floor.
